# Figma API Configuration
# Required for: token sync (FIGMA_FILE_KEY + FIGMA_ACCESS_TOKEN), component metadata script (FIGMA_ACCESS_TOKEN only)
#
# To obtain a Figma Access Token (free; rate limits apply by plan):
# 1. In Figma: your avatar (top right) → Settings
# 2. Scroll to "Personal access tokens" → Generate new token
# 3. Copy the token and paste it below (store in .env, never commit)
#
# To find your Figma File Key (for token sync):
# 1. Open your Figma design system file
# 2. The file key is in the URL: https://www.figma.com/file/FILE_KEY/... or .../design/FILE_KEY/...
# 3. Copy the FILE_KEY and paste it below
#
# Optional: run "node scripts/figma-component-meta.js <Figma URL>" to fetch component description + link.

FIGMA_FILE_KEY=your-figma-file-key-here
FIGMA_ACCESS_TOKEN=your-figma-access-token-here
